Interface IndexingDecorator<T,​W extends Writable<W>>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Directory<W>, IndexDirectory<T,​W>, Writable<W>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractIndexingDecorator, DateIndexingDecorator, HourIndexingDecorator, IndexingDecoratorOnDisk
    public interface IndexingDecorator<T,​W extends Writable<W>>
extends IndexDirectory<T,​W>
    An IndexDirectoryDecorator that writes a file called "index", containing a JSON array containing all elements returned by IndexDirectoryOnDisk.getIndex(app.coronawarn.server.services.distribution.assembly.structure.util.ImmutableStack<java.lang.Object>), formatted with the IndexDirectoryOnDisk.getIndexFormatter() on Writable.prepare(app.coronawarn.server.services.distribution.assembly.structure.util.ImmutableStack<java.lang.Object>).
